<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>54</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Na Lalchutphah leh Lallukhuk Na hun taihsan,
 Khawvela kei dinga Na hungin;
 Mahleh Nang dingin Bethlehem ah mun um lo,
 Na pienna mun thiengtho dingin.

[V2]
 Hungin, ka lungah, Lal Isu!
 Nang din mun ka lunggil ah a um;
 Hungin, ka lunggil ah, Lal Isu!
 Nang din mun ka lunggil ah a um.

[V3]
 2. Angelte lasak in van In chu a thawng hi,
 Na Lal lopizie chu a phuong ui;
 Ahih ziekin, pien dan niemin lei ah Na hung,
 Hahpia hung kingainiem in.

[V4]
 3. Si-al ten kuo a nei, Vachaten bu a nei,
 Gamnuoi a sawlthing buk limnuoi ah;
 Nang Pathien Chapa kuolna vang hampa ahi,
 Galili-a gamgaw a chun.

[V5]
 4. Lalpa, Nang na hunga, Thuhing chuh Na hun puoi,
 Na mite suohchakna ding thu chuh;
 Mahleh muhsit a umin, linglukhuk chu khun,
 Kalvari-ah a hun pui ui.

[V6]
 Hungin, ka lungah Lal Isu!
 Nangmah kross mai chuh ken ka suong hi;
 Hungin, ka lunggil ah, Lal Isu!
 Nangmah kross mai chuh ken ka suong hi.

[V7]
 5. Van khawpi kipak a lapawl kasak tieng leh,
 Guolzo a Nang na hung kit tiengleh,
 Na aw chun tihin ei sam hen &quot;Nanga dingin
 Ka kawmah mun a um ie&quot; tin.

[V8]
 Ka lung kipak ding, Lal Isu!
 Na hunga kei nei hun sap tieng leh;
 Ka lung kipak tana Lal Isu!
 Na hung,a kei nei hun sap tieng leh.</lyrics>
<title>ROOM FOR THEE</title>
</song>